{
  "stem": "942.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Saturday evening in the summer, we went again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In the winter, we usually stayed at home on Saturday evening, and we had our services, you know, between the three families-- my grandfather, uncle, and my father.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And life was pretty good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I had many friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We had a lot of fun.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had much space to play around in our own house, in the lumber shed, and we had an old stable.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we were playing, I remember, cowboys and bandits.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had all these books, you know, about cowboys and bandits.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we were not allowed to read these books, in fact.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I remember I had to read these books sort of secretly because when my father found these books, he used to take them away from me and tear them up.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, his objection was that it was not the right thing to read.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I had to keep my mind on, on, on the learning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had a real problem, especially with the Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The teacher wanted me to learn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He wanted to show my father that he's doing a real good job.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this teacher had a stick you know that he was-- he was really giving us the works with this stick.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember many a day that I was going home with a real bad-- he used to hit me, and I used to get a nose bleed, and my shirt was full of blood.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And if I complained at home, I used to get some more from my father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was the type of thing that went on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I did not sort of [INAUDIBLE] to this particular type of thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember many friends of mine that they were really fantastic in Hebrew learning.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
